events.text: You try to complete the mega square. However it has some holes…
Bam! The entire mega square falls apart as you couldn’t make it whole.
Why did we even invite a hexagon!
GUYS! This is a party, don’t be so mean!
Sorry Hex, looks like it didn’t work out.
This is so embarassing, I hope they won't think bad of other hexagons now.
That’s something… Why do they want to be a hexagon? Being a hexagon sucks.
